<subSubSection id="B88331D9FF9FFF68B5E63958210E02C1" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="F0266252FF9FFF68B5E63958210E02C1" blockId="5.[136,1452,551,758]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">
The original collection cited by 
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B497395822C00276" author="Bentham, G." box="[505,690,551,578]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" pagination="226 - 228" refId="ref7178" refString="Bentham, G. (1870) Caesalpinieae. In: von Martius, C. F. P. &amp; Eichler, A. G. (Eds.) Flora Brasiliensis 15 (2). F. Fleischer, Leipzig, pp. 226 - 228." type="book chapter" year="1870">Bentham (1870)</bibRefCitation>
for 
<taxonomicName id="379919D1FF9FFF68B78A395724640276" authority=", Spruce 2021" authorityName=", Spruce" authorityYear="2021" box="[740,1046,551,578]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Eperua" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leucantha">
<emphasis id="C2EDBE40FF9FFF68B78A395723060275" box="[740,884,551,577]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">E. leucantha</emphasis>
, Spruce 2021
</taxonomicName>
, combined collections made in two different dates: 
<date id="84274492FF9FFF68B4553934219D0252" box="[315,495,587,614]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" value="1851-12">December 1851</date>
and 
<date id="84274492FF9FFF68B747393322B60252" box="[553,708,587,614]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" value="1852-01">January 1852</date>
. However, in order to comprise a single gathering the specimens need to be collected on the same date (
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B73F3910234502BE" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[593,823,623,650]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" refId="ref8934" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Regnum Vegetabile 159. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten, 254 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="C2EDBE40FF9FFF68B7DB390F228202BD" box="[693,752,623,649]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
). Thus, Spruce 2021 must be considered two different collections. As 
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B45B39EC219E029A" author="Bentham, G." box="[309,492,659,686]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" pagination="226 - 228" refId="ref7178" refString="Bentham, G. (1870) Caesalpinieae. In: von Martius, C. F. P. &amp; Eichler, A. G. (Eds.) Flora Brasiliensis 15 (2). F. Fleischer, Leipzig, pp. 226 - 228." type="book chapter" year="1870">Bentham (1870)</bibRefCitation>
did not specify the collection date of Spruce 2021, the exsiccate K000555107 with a handwritten annotation by Spruce is not the 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B71539C822AF02E5" box="[635,733,695,721]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">holotype</typeStatus>
as informed by 
<bibRefCitation id="94081FA3FF9FFF68B6FB39C7244802E6" author="Cowan, R. S." box="[917,1082,695,722]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194" pagination="1 - 45" refId="ref7339" refString="Cowan, R. S. (1975) Monograph of the genus Eperua (Leguminosae: Caesalpinioideae). Smithsonian Contributions to Botany 28: 1 - 45. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 0081024 X. 28" type="journal article" year="1975">Cowan (1975)</bibRefCitation>
. We correct here Cowan’s use of 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B5E639A4209802C1" box="[136,234,731,757]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">holotype</typeStatus>
to 
<typeStatus id="2F22DCF0FF9FFF68B46039A4210A02C1" box="[270,376,731,757]" pageId="5" pageNumber="194">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
